resetBridgeCounters.t.sol
├── given sender does not have the relevant role
│  └── it should revert with AccessManagedUnauthorized
└── given sender has the relevant role
   ├── given no spoke caliber was registered in this contract for the provided chain ID
   │  └── it should revert with InvalidChainID
   └── given a spoke caliber was registered in this contract for the provided chain ID
      ├── it should erase all the existing bridge counters for the given chainid and token, in machine storage
      └── it should emit a ResetBridgeCounters event
